#. module: photography
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:photography.homepage
msgid ""
"<span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">Welcome to Frozen Moments Photography, "
"where every click freezes a moment in time. We specialize in </span>\n"
"                  <strong>\n"
"                    <span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">capturing the essence "
"of life's most beautiful moments</span>\n"
"                  </strong>\n"
"                  <span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"> through the lens of our "
"cameras.</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">Te damos la bienvenida a Estudio Hollywood, "
"aquí siempre te haremos lucir como una estrella. Nos especializamos en </"
"span>\n"
"                  <strong>\n"
"                    <span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">capturar la esencia de "
"los momentos más hermosos de tu vida</span>\n"
"                  </strong>\n"
"                  <span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"> a través del lente de "
"nuestras cámaras.</span>"

#. module: photography
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:photography.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Accounting</strong>: do more than simple invoicing - with Odoo "
"Accounting, you can generate tax reports, manage your invoices and bills and "
"even synchronize payments from your bank account automatically"
msgstr ""
"<strong>Contabilidad</strong>: La aplicación Contabilidad de Odoo no se "
"limita a las funciones básicas, puede generar reportes fiscales, gestionar "
"sus facturas e incluso sincronizar pagos en automático desde su cuenta "
"bancaria."

#. module: photography
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:photography.ir_ui_view_1960
msgid ""
"<strong>And more</strong>: Whatever your occasion or preference, I can help "
"you create photos that suit your needs and expectations."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Y mucho más...</strong> Sea cual sea la ocasión o sus preferencias, "
"le ayudaré a crear fotos que se adapten a sus necesidades y expectativas."

#. module: photography
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:photography.ir_ui_view_1959
msgid ""
"<strong>Attract and retain talent</strong> by showcasing your company "
"culture and work environment;"
msgstr ""
"<strong>Atraiga y conserve el mejor talento</strong>, muestre la cultura y "
"el ambiente laboral de su empresa."

#. module: photography
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:photography.ir_ui_view_1960
msgid ""
"<strong>Baby portraits</strong>: Capture the cuteness and innocence of your "
"baby with adorable photos that will make you smile every time you look at "
"them;"
msgstr ""
"<strong>Retratos de bebés</strong>: Capture la ternura e inocencia de su "
"bebé con fotos adorables que le harán sonreír cada que las mire."

#. module: photography
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:photography.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Email Marketing </strong>and <strong>Social Marketing</strong> "
"<span>: reach out to your clients regarding special events or offers, or "
"prospect for new clients​</span><strong>​</strong>​<strong>​</strong>"
msgstr ""
"<strong>Marketing por correo</strong> y <strong>Redes sociales</"
"strong><span>: comunícate con tus clientes y avísales sobre tus eventos u "
"ofertas especiales. También puedes prospectar nuevos clientes.​</span><strong>​"
"</strong>​<strong>​</strong>"

#. module: photography
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:photography.ir_ui_view_1959
msgid ""
"<strong>Enhance your reputation and credibility</strong> by documenting your "
"achievements and social responsibility;"
msgstr ""
"<strong>Mejore su reputación y credibilidad</strong>, documente sus logros y "
"responsabilidad social."

#. module: photography
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:photography.ir_ui_view_1960
msgid ""
"<strong>Family portraits</strong>: Preserve your precious memories and show "
"your family bond with stunning photos that you can cherish for years to come;"
msgstr ""
"<strong>Retratos familiares</strong>: Guarde preciosos recuerdos y muestre "
"su vínculo familiar con impresionantes fotos que podrá atesorar durante "
"años. "

#. module: photography
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:photography.ir_ui_view_1959
msgid ""
"<strong>Increase your sales and conversions</strong> by highlighting your "
"products’ features and benefits;"
msgstr ""
"<strong>Aumente sus ventas y conversiones</strong> al mostrar las "
"características y beneficios de sus productos."

#. module: photography
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:photography.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Planning</strong>: manage plannings for team members and resources, "
"like a studio room or some hardware"
msgstr ""
"<strong>Planeación</strong>: Gestione la planeación de los miembros del "
"equipo y los recursos, como una sala de estudio o algún material."

#. module: photography
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:photography.ir_ui_view_1960
msgid ""
"<strong>Professional portraits</strong>: Impress your clients and employers "
"with polished and confident photos that reflect your personal brand and "
"expertise;"
msgstr ""
"<strong>Retratos profesionales</strong>: Impresione a sus clientes y "
"empleadores con fotos elegantes y confiables que reflejen su marca personal "
"y experiencia"

#. module: photography
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:photography.welcome_article_body
